    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Agenda</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>What?? Fiddler?</li>
            <li>How to use Fiddler properly</li>
            <li>Not well-known features</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Fiddler</h2>
